videos.headline: Penn State fools Michigan with fake punt
videos.description: Penn State punter Jordan Stout executes a fake punt perfectly as the Nittany Lions pick up a first down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State fools Michigan with fake punt) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State fumbles the ball away on fake field goal
videos.description: After a successful fake punt earlier, Penn State tries for a fake field goal play, but turns the ball over on a fumble.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State fumbles the ball away on fake field goal) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: McNamara throws strike to Wilson for Michigan TD
videos.description: Michigan QB Cade McNamara caps off a 7:30 drive with a 21-yard touchdown pass to Roman Wilson.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McNamara throws strike to Wilson for Michigan TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: McNamara finds Wilson again for another Michigan TD
videos.description: Michigan QB Cade McNamara lasers a pass to Roman Wilson for their second touchdown connection of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McNamara finds Wilson again for another Michigan TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clifford throws TD pass, 2-point conversion to tie game for PSU
videos.description: Penn State QB Sean Clifford connects with Tyler Warren for a touchdown and then finds Jahan Dotson to convert the two-point conversion.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clifford throws TD pass, 2-point conversion to tie game for PSU) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State fans erupt after defense recovers a fumble
videos.description: The Penn State defense forces a sack and fumble on Cade McNamara, and the Nittany Lions recover the ball.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State fans erupt after defense recovers a fumble) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Erick All barely gets across pylon for Michigan's go-ahead TD
videos.description: Michigan QB Cade McNamara passes to Erick All, who runs 47 yards and barely gets the ball across the pylon for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Erick All barely gets across pylon for Michigan's go-ahead TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET
